{"tid":188700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仙氣美女揸巴士出更！網民讚貌似游BB 巴迷開live睹芳容","createTime":"2017-04-06T01:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T01:52:37.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f687c3c84a3a609481fc7e5541aa9e845eb1eddf","tid":188700,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T01:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170405/large/1491397882_9da6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F1491397882_9da6.png&h=a76ccb81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170405/large/1491400294_94a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F1491400294_94a4.jpg&h=064477db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170405/large/1491400292_f55c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170405%2Flarge%2F1491400292_f55c.jpg&h=d278007f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n城巴新聘的靚女車長出更，近日成為巴迷界熱話，吸引部分傳媒追訪。開工僅第7天的80後女車長阿穎，擁有一把啡色長髮，不時掛上甜美笑容，難怪迷倒不少男巴迷，有網民讚她是全港最靚女的巴士司機，無出其右，更有人認為她貌似本土派女神游蕙禎或日本女星山本美月。有巴迷昨蜂擁到巴士站，等候她開工，甚至在facebook專頁直播，亦有休班城巴司機慕名而來，盼一睹芳容。<br />\n<br />\n阿穎向傳媒透露，她原本從事飲食業，但因很喜歡揸巴士，考車牌已滿3年，符合車長入職條件，決定轉行，獲城巴安排駕駛小西灣至中環的789路線。<br />\n【網民點睇】<br />\nRandy Liong 有啲似（日本女星）山本美月<br />\nHarry Mak：個車長個樣有幾分似游蕙禎XD<br />\nWong Yuen Chuen：香港巴士司機中佢最靚女，無出其右<br />\nRyo Saeba：遲啲唔使揸啦，做城巴大使<br />\nDick Sin：我驚女車長會冇咗份工"},{"pid":"eb6c046900e92827303a590ca1ea60cadc49e1ce","tid":188700,"uid":41606,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T01:20:44.000Z","msg":"司機靚過游b"},{"pid":"2ec6a3b8c18abd7c9d5fff7cddb8978f238e1c08","tid":188700,"uid":1192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T01:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲啲唔使揸啦，做城巴大使</blockquote><br />\n依句真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇吓9A車長就知"},{"pid":"e72ec3e486faa1a4db10f8298ea1b2f3c43c0d01","tid":188700,"uid":20828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T01:24:44.000Z","msg":"事實證明樣靚真係特別啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266c1dc3410a07cb24441dc59d08d5727fb99c90","tid":188700,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T01:36:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事實證明樣靚真係特別啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普通樣喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過係冇女既行業豬西都變女神"},{"pid":"d77a67d2b615ae28de12f0e5bd96d0be1c393081","tid":188700,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T01:52:30.000Z","msg":"角度問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c833dfc7bcdbfe219849a5be7245077436aa15","tid":188700,"uid":37384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T01:52:37.000Z","msg":"好樣過油雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁撚樣侮辱個女司機為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}